metadata.author: Shark Cafe
metadata.description:
Paint along to chill lo-fi beats as you create a dreamy, starry mountain landscape, using something called atmospheric perspective. Learn the science behind how the Purkinje effect causes our eyes to see colors differently at night, real-life stargazing tips, and more!

This tutorial has been tested against both kid-quality and professional-quality materials, so rest assured - this is perfect for all ages and abilities. 

A digital step-by-step visual guide is included as reference, which can be downloaded from the product listing page on the Yoto Card Store.
